I really appreciate the quality and design of this controller. It has more features then a fully loaded Scuf for half the price. The addition of software really makes this controller unique in regards to pro controllers. The biggest fault of pro controllers is durability so I am hoping a licensed product by Sony has some longevity.

reviews: This was the first time a bought a cologne with a less recognizable name and I regret it.

I bought these based off the good reviews. My opinion is they are over hyped the headline "Premium Soft Cotton" is misleading. Compared to other "premium boxers" brands these fall flat. But what can you expect 6 pairs for $30 compared to other premium brands that charge $30 for one pair. In conclusion, these boxers are very average you are not purchasing a high quality item at a low price.

Although it says it works for all shoes it actually only working for running shoes. I bought them for my skateboard shoes but they didn't fit they did however fit in my running shoes. I used to always wear skate shoes because they slip on easy, but enjoy my runners much more now that they are slip on and weigh much less then the skate shoe.
These are great for someone learning piano I have learned how to play songs much faster with this product.

For someone who is heavy handed this product is amazing. So great not snapping pieces of lead all the time. I used to always write with .7mm lead to avoid this but this is a much better solution. You can write much finer and neater with .5mm my math is much more legible now.

This product has some of the worst manufacturing quality control. I order this item during assembly some of the threaded holes in the frame were cut so poorly, the bolts only threaded half way into the socket or were angled and stripped the bolt. Amazon quickly sent me a replacement and I sent the defective one back. Waited another week only to find out the second one I got had the same problems in different locations. It is tragic because the bench looks like it would be a good piece of workout equipment.

review_title: If you plan to solve it more then once I would suggest looking at better cubes
reviews:
I just recently bought an actual speed cube prompting me to write a quick review about this product. This definitely not a speed cube this is a puzzle. Its fun but serves no real purpose after you learn to solve it, since you can not really improve on faster solves. It was a decent beginner cube but way overpriced. The best speed cubes on the market are approximately the same price. In conclusion, this was a good cube for a short period of time but if your someone who likes to constantly improve. This cubes ability to keep up with your skill level is poor and it is overpriced compared to actual speed cubes.

Update: aGreatlife has superb customer service !

If you are looking at buying this product, it is probably because your original charger has kicked the bucket. I have bought three different chargers for my Macbook pro they all eventually stop working. My guess why they stop working is because of poor design. Apple and other brands stick to keeping the power block as small as possible in the shape of a square. Which results in overheating and eventual malfunction where as the rectangular design allows for better heat dispersion.
